# =============================================================================
# Brewfile - Homebrew Bundle Configuration (DEPRECATED)
# =============================================================================
#
# ⚠️  DEPRECATION NOTICE
# This file has been split into two separate files for better cross-platform support:
#
#   - Brewfile.common: Cross-platform packages (macOS & Linux)
#   - Brewfile.macos:  macOS-specific GUI applications (cask)
#
# Usage:
#   macOS:  make install  (installs both Brewfile.common + Brewfile.macos)
#   Linux:  make install  (installs only Brewfile.common)
#
# Manual installation:
#   brew bundle install --file=installers/Brewfile.common
#   brew bundle install --file=installers/Brewfile.macos  # macOS only
#
# This file is kept for backward compatibility but should not be used directly.
# It will be removed in a future version.
# =============================================================================

# For actual package definitions, see:
# - installers/Brewfile.common  (cross-platform packages)
# - installers/Brewfile.macos   (macOS-specific applications)
